;whois nick - Tells you the rank of someone
;notice nick message - Sends a notice to an user
;todo - Tells you the todo list for UBot
;join #channel - Makes the bot join a channel
;rank nick rank - Promoted/demotes an user (normal, trusted, operator, admin)
;rawtext - Toggles raw text output into console
;reload - Reloads tables from perms.json, todo.json and help.json
